About this item The Dell Refurbished Laptop PC E5420 has everything you need to compute on the go. Microsoft Windows 7 Professional lets you complete any task.
Dell Refurbished 14" E5420 Laptop PC: Key Features and Benefits: Intel Core i5 processor 2.50GHz 4GB DDR2 SDRAM system memory The laptop with Intel core i5 processor 4GB memory gives you the power to handle most power-hungry applications and tons of multimedia work 128GB SSD hard drive Store 85,000 photos, 36,000 songs or 67 hours of HD video and more DVD-RW drive Watch movies and read and write CDs and DVDs in multiple formats on this Dell 14" laptop 10/100/1000Mbps Gigabit Ethernet, 802.11b Wireless LAN Connect to a broadband modem with wired Ethernet or wirelessly connect to a WiFi signal or hotspot with the 802.11b connection built into your PC 14" WXGA HD display The Dell 14" laptop has integrated Intel GMA 4500M HD Graphics
Dell Refurbished Laptop PC E5420 Additional Features: The laptop with Intel core i5 processor 4GB memory has 4 x USB 2.0 ports, 1 x FireWire (1394) port, 1 x audio-out jack, 1 x microphone jack, 1 x RJ-45 Ethernet port, 1 x VGA port Standard lithium-ion battery 1 HDMI Port 4.5 lbs, 13.8" x 9.5" x 1.3"
Software: Windows 7 Professional 64-Bit Edition (To learn more about the features of Windows 7, click here) Backup and Restore options built into Windows allow you to create safety copies of your most important personal files, so you're always prepared for the worst
Dell Refurbished Laptop PC E5420 Support and Warranty: Refurbished items have a 1-year parts and labor limited warranty Recovery partition on Hard Drive
What's In The Box: Power cord and AC adapter Standard lithium-ion battery Quick Start Guide
